95
00:08:13,050 --> 00:08:14,427
Yukata.

96
00:08:14,451 --> 00:08:15,771
Look.

97
00:08:15,772 --> 00:08:18,146
I got a present from Dad.

98
00:08:18,675 --> 00:08:21,534
I will use these colors to draw a lot.

99
00:08:21,675 --> 00:08:22,902
