100
00:08:23,449 --> 00:08:25,449
Yukata, you should draw something too.

101
00:08:25,473 --> 00:08:26,752
What should I draw?

102
00:08:26,776 --> 00:08:28,241
Draw a reindeer.

103
00:08:28,632 --> 00:08:29,976
Oh, Yukata, welcome...

104
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:32,312
Tane, come here.

105
00:08:32,547 --> 00:08:34,104
