259
00:19:03,266 --> 00:19:04,310
Hmm?

260
00:19:10,016 --> 00:19:11,283
Minoru,

261
00:19:11,689 --> 00:19:13,185
you seem to be good at drawing.

262
00:19:13,630 --> 00:19:14,572
Why?

263
00:19:16,689 --> 00:19:18,791
The rice balls' faces were so cute.

264
00:19:19,639 --> 00:19:21,331
Oh, really?

265
00:19:21,694 --> 00:19:23,696
Next time, I'll draw something, then.

266
00:19:24,079 --> 00:19:25,931
Okay, I want to see it.

267
00:19:29,886 --> 00:19:32,471
Time flies.
It's already the end of the year.

268
00:19:34,268 --> 00:19:35,708
Right.

269
00:19:36,909 --> 00:19:39,311
Will your family stay at home?

270
00:19:39,686 --> 00:19:41,614
Yeah, what about you?

271
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:44,483
The New Year's Eve,
or the New Year's Day.

272
00:19:45,661 --> 00:19:46,686
Um...

273
00:19:48,446 --> 00:19:52,758
